summary: RektSkulls: Bringing Compete-To-Earn Web3 Game Powered by Deflationary REKT Token - RektSkulls is a gamified ecosystem centered around the REKT token, which is exclusively generated through staking native NFT collection, strong burn mechanics, and varied utilities. The project aims to revolutionize the gamefi industry by introducing a compete-to-earn (C2E) model based on a subscription system.
